channel.title: I fixed my problem Mod please lock or remove
channel.description:
I made a server and had it port forwarded. It worked fine for a while until I stopped turning it on while I went on Vacation. When I got back I cannot log in and no one else can either. I had many people play on my server before this. Anyone know what might have happened? :confused: :confused: :confused:
BTW my server source was allstar scape but then I tried other sources and it still didn't work. The compiler says nothing is wrong with the code. No Errors. 317 server
Any suggestions helpful Thank you.
~Owner Death
